PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION unto Her Majesty whereby the WOODLAND CREE BAND surrenders, for an indefinite term, all of its rights and interests in the oil and gas that may be found on Woodland Cree Indian Reserves No. 226, 227 and 228, in the Province of Alberta, for the purpose of granting leases, permits and exploration licences.
Attachments
precis:
Acceptance of a DESIGNATION unto Her Majesty whereby the WOODLAND CREE BAND
surrenders, for an indefinite term, all of its rights and interests in the
oil and gas that may be found on Woodland Cree Indian Reserves No. 226, 227
and 228, in the Province of Alberta, for the purpose of granting leases,
permits and exploration licences.
